original_title: RFVideo Face Off Vol. 11: Big Lips & Shaking Hips
overview: Let me give you two names and you tell me what comes to your mind…  Missy Hyatt and The Honky Tonk Man… controversial comes to my mind.  When RF VIDEO sets out to conduct a new interview for our Face Off series we make sure we are going to give you a good bang for your buck..no pun intended there Missy.
title: RFVideo Face Off Vol. 11: Big Lips & Shaking Hips
